title: Khu Phra Khu Nang
overview: Orphan Din loves to sing and dance Yikay; it's at the centre of his life and soul. The path to Yikay hero, however, is not easy. Being faced with the disdain of others only ignites Din's ambition to climb from the earth to the stars. His vision of the life he wants includes Sano, a persevering young woman and his biggest supporter. From earth to the stars she's loved him alone, before he was beloved by many.
